## COMPONENTES — PADRÕES

### Botão primário
```tsx
<motion.button
  whileTap={{ scale: 0.97 }}
  whileHover={{ scale: 1.01 }}
  className="w-full h-12 rounded-full bg-[var(--q-accent-8)] text-white font-medium text-base tracking-wide transition-shadow hover:shadow-[var(--q-shadow-glow-accent)]"
>
  {children}
</motion.button>
```

### Card
```tsx
<motion.div
  variants={VARIANTS.cardReveal}
  whileHover={{ y: -2, transition: { duration: 0.15 } }}
  className="rounded-[var(--q-radius-lg)] bg-[var(--q-bg-surface)] border border-[var(--q-border-default)] p-5"
>
```

### Texto de conteúdo (direction, affirmation, reflection)
```tsx
<p className="font-[family-name:var(--font-instrument)] text-2xl text-[var(--q-text-primary)] leading-relaxed italic">
  {content.direction}
</p>
```

### Input
```tsx
<input className="w-full h-12 px-4 rounded-[var(--q-radius-md)] bg-[var(--q-bg-raised)] border border-[var(--q-border-default)] text-[var(--q-text-primary)] placeholder:text-[var(--q-text-tertiary)] focus:outline-none focus:border-[var(--q-accent-8)] transition-colors" />
```

